      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行强烈支持欧盟财政规则的纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-strongly-backs-discipline-on-eu-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行坚决支持欧盟推动债务国家的预算政策符合该地区的财政规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-strongly-backs-discipline-on-eu-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
